-- Peru Stocks: Buenaventura, Edegel, Minsur, Panoro, Siderperu
-- B y   A l e x   E m e r y
-- 2012-01-27T19:11:05Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-27/peru-stocks-buenaventura-edegel-minsur-panoro-siderperu.html
The following companies are having
unusual price changes in  Peru  trading. Stock symbols are in
parentheses and share prices are as of 1:29 p.m. local time.  The  Lima General Index (IGBVL)  rose for a fifth straight day,
gaining 0.5 percent to 21,760.77. The  MSCI All Peru Capped Index (MXPECAPD) 
climbed 0.3 percent to 2,795.67.  Industrial stocks gained after Peruvian companies and the
government raised more than $1.8 billion from debt offerings
this week, said Hernando Pastor, an analyst at Lima-based Kallpa
Securities SAB.  Corp. Aceros Arequipa SA (CORA)  (CORAREI1 PE), the Lima-based
steelmaker, jumped 5 percent to 2.31 soles.  Cementos Pacasmayo
SAA (CPACASI1)  (CPACASC1 PE), the Hochschild Group’s cement producer, rose
for a fifth session, adding 3.1 percent to 6.6 soles.  Edegel SA (EDE) 
(EDEGELC1 PE), the Peruvian unit of  Spain ’s Endesa SA, advanced
1.1 percent to 1.85 soles after  Fitch Ratings  said Peru’s
electricity industry will invest in expansion plans.  Empresa
Siderurgica del Peru SAA  (SIDERC1 PE), a unit of Gerdau SA known
as Siderperu, climbed 1.1 percent to 90 centimos.  Miners gained after gold, silver and tin advanced.  Rio Cristal Resources Corp. (RCZ)  , a Canadian
exploration company, rose 7.7 percent to 14 cents, a three-month
high.  Cia. de Minas Buenaventura SAA  (BVN PE), the country’s
biggest precious-metals miner, gained for the fourth session in
five, adding 3.3 percent to $43.38.  Panoro Minerals Ltd. (PML)  , a Canadian copper and gold exploration company, climbed 1.7
percent to 61 cents.  Minsur SA (MINSURI1)  (MINSURI1 PE), the world’s
fourth-largest tin producer, rose for a fifth day, adding 1.3
percent to 3.03 soles.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Alex Emery in Lima at 
 aemery1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
